Did King Arthur really exist? At some point, questions like this become difficult to 
answer ... with his best knight, Lancelot du Lac; a wizard advisor named Merlin; 
an evil half sister, Morgan le Fay; a famous sword called Excalibur -- and so on.

Feb 12, 2016 ... The legend of King Arthur and the Knights of the Round Table ... CLIMAX; 
Arthur's half-sister, Morgana Le Fay, threatens Camelot and Arthur ... Morgana's 
evil works against Arthur in the battles, but Merlin is more powerful.
